data.description: Endless opportunity awaits in this Westfield gem of an investment property with the potential for a low interest rate w/assumable mortgage! Whether you are looking to expand your portfolio or seeking an owner occupant arrangement, this expansive multi-family home in a town with great schools, commutability and a vibrant downtown awaits its lucky new owner! Second floor unit will be vacant by end of April. Updated from the inside out, this home boasts 2 generously sized apartment units with hardwood floors - each featuring 3 bedrooms, an eat-in kitchen with granite counters, 1 full bath, dishwasher, and a washer/dryer. Large third-floor attic (bonus room) can be used for an office or storage by the second floor unit. The unfinished walkout basement provides excellent storage! Fenced in backyard has paver patio, storage shed, and large yard. Landlord pays water, sewer, garbage and maintenance. Live worry-free with upgrades just 4 years old - roof, HVAC units, windows and much more! Conveniently located near mass transportation (making commuting a breeze), parks with basketball courts, major highways, house of worship, award-winning schools, downtown Westfield and more!
